AT.name: Rorrim
AT.description: Rorrim is a puzzle/maze game suitable for all ages. Help the princess escape the dungeon both in the mirror world and the real one. Use both the Wii U™ GamePad and the TV to see both realities at the same time to get through the dungeon alive. Post on Miiverse™ from within the game, along with Stamps you can collect along the way.
